      <a class="btn secondary" href="v3-reporting.html">Worldwide Reporting</a>
      <a class="btn secondary" href="v3-reporting-australia.html">Australia Reporting</a>
    </div>

    <div class="callout center-callout">
      You do not need the whole plan right now. You only need the next right move.
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="card center-card">
    <h2>If you still feel overwhelmed</h2>

    <p class="note">
      If you are struggling to know what matters most right now, start with the pages below.
    </p>

    <div class="btn-grid btn-grid-soft">
      <a class="btn" href="v3-what-now.html">What To Do Now</a>
      <a class="btn secondary" href="v3-real-scenarios.html">Real Scenarios</a>
      <a class="btn secondary" href="v3-parent-scripts.html">Parent Scripts</a>
      <a class="btn secondary" href="v3-reporting.html">Report &amp; Get Help</a>
    </div>

    <div class="callout center-callout">
      If the risk feels active, serious, or escalating, move toward evidence preservation and reporting sooner rather than later.
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="card hero-warning center-card">
    <h2>Help another parent stay calm and act earlier</h2>

    <div class="rule-box">
      <p>Many parents make harder situations worse simply because no one showed them what to do first.</p>
      <p>Sharing a page like this can help another family move from panic into protection.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="danger-line">
      A calmer first response can change the outcome
